<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.9">
<l>collāy tirumārvā vuṉakkākit toṇṭupaṭṭa</l>
<l>nallē ṉaiviṉaikaḷ naliyāmai nampunampī</l>
<l>mallā kuṭamāṭī matucūta ṉēyulakil</l>
<l>cellā nallicaiyāy tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with Tiru at your chest, promise that karma not afflict me,</l>
<l>A good [person] who undertook service for your sake,</l>
<l>Noble, strong [lord], pot dancer, Madhusūdana,</l>
<l>You who is subtle music which does not occur in [this] world,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
